ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mobilize-uploads-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/u
 ploads/event/Capitol%20cropped_20260320230559319502.jpg
DESCRIPTION:There are competitive primaries this year in two of the three 
 new congressional districts (CA-01 and CA-04) that fall within Sonoma Coun
 ty and Indivisible Sonoma County is working to endorse in each. As part of
  that effort\, we are reaching out to the four candidates and are hoping t
 o secure their participation in a candidate forum\, in person\, at our nex
 t general meeting. Following the meeting\, active Indivisible Sonoma Count
 y members* will be asked to take part in our endorsement vote. Stay tune
LOCATION:Finley Community Center: Santa Rosa Recreation & Parks\, 2060 W C
 ollege Ave\, Santa Rosa\, CA\, 95401
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblesonomacounty/event/924951/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Sonoma County (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
